          <div class="grid-4">
            <i class="icon blog">&nbsp;</i>
            <h3>
              NGC Magazine
            </h3>
            <p>
              <a href="http://www.ngcmagazine.ca/?utm_campaign=ngcmagazine&amp;utm_medium=ngc&amp;utm_source=galleryca&amp;utm_content=onlineextras" title="NGC Magazine" target="_blank">The National Gallery of Canada’s online magazine&nbsp;- a frequently updated source of information about the Canadian art world and the goings-on at the National Gallery of Canada.</a>
            </p><i class="icon newsletter">&nbsp;</i>
            <h3>
              Newsletter
            </h3>
            <p>
              <a href="http://eepurl.com/nYeyP">&nbsp;Subscribe to our e-newsletter. Receive a monthly email summary of important information and current events. A great way to stay on top of everything that's going on at the Gallery!</a>
            </p><i class="icon webcam">&nbsp;</i>
            <h3>
              Webcam
            </h3>
            <p>
